WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.880 --> 00:00:04.880
You're not very clean, my darling !

00:00:05.340 --> 00:00:07.960
But believe me, I've seen worse,

00:00:08.340 --> 00:00:10.840
I'm going to turn you, you little sow

00:00:11.060 --> 00:00:13.180
Into the purest sapphire

00:00:13.180 --> 00:00:14.680
It's freezing!

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:17.120
It would've been warmer if you had arrived on time.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.620
First of all, scrub you well

00:00:20.620 --> 00:00:23.380
Soap, rinse and polish

00:00:23.380 --> 00:00:26.280
This is my instantaneous recipe

00:00:26.280 --> 00:00:28.520
For you to marry in honor

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:30.100
Mulan, what's this?

00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:33.460
Notes, in case I forget something?

00:00:33.460 --> 00:00:36.760
Hold this! We'll need more luck than I thought.

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:39.900
You'll see, thanks to us

00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:42.620
You'll make all the boys go mad, sweetie

00:00:42.620 --> 00:00:45.500
By combing your hair, with so much taste

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:48.620
You'll bring honor to us all.

00:00:49.140 --> 00:00:51.860
A girl can bring her family

00:00:51.860 --> 00:00:54.460
Great honor by marriage

00:00:54.460 --> 00:00:57.440
By striking a good match,

00:00:57.440 --> 00:01:00.340
She wins the match !

00:01:00.520 --> 00:01:03.280
Boys like girls

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:05.980
Calm and obedient, agile-minded

00:01:05.980 --> 00:01:08.600
Delicate and subtle, with a tiny waist

00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:11.480
You'll bring honor to us all!

00:01:12.060 --> 00:01:18.080
We all must serve our Emperor, who guards us from the Huns

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:20.580
Men by fighting

00:01:20.580 --> 00:01:23.380
Women by giving birth

00:01:23.740 --> 00:01:26.580
Finishing touch, fatal lips

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:29.160
Like a lotus blossom soft and pale

00:01:29.160 --> 00:01:31.940
You'll make an ideal wife

00:01:31.940 --> 00:01:35.340
You'll bring honor to us all!

00:01:38.740 --> 00:01:40.740
There, you're exquisite

00:01:40.740 --> 00:01:44.600
Not yet. An apple for serenity

00:01:44.600 --> 00:01:46.940
a pendant for balance,

00:01:46.940 --> 00:01:52.160
Beads of Jade to dress

00:01:52.160 --> 00:01:57.480
Proudly your beauty

00:01:57.480 --> 00:02:02.980
With this lucky locust

00:02:02.980 --> 00:02:05.640
I forbid you any mistake !

00:02:05.980 --> 00:02:08.700
Dear ancestors, help me

00:02:08.700 --> 00:02:11.640
I must not do even one misstep

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:14.440
If I disappointed the Fa family

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:18.360
My father would lose his honor...

00:02:18.620 --> 00:02:21.280
Afflicted of an awful terror,

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:24.180
We are meeting the matchmaker

00:02:24.180 --> 00:02:26.780
Destiny, be coaxing

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:29.460
With these pretty China dolls

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:32.160
Mandarin with opaline skin

00:02:32.180 --> 00:02:35.800
Who come offering you their hearts !

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:41.880
Bring honor to us

00:02:41.880 --> 00:02:46.820
To us all, Honor and Happiness

